values: Well I decided to make a Live Journal. Why? I don't Know why. Anyways, David called me a hour ago telling me he was an hour away from camp. God I miss him so much!! And bridget,melinda and my peachies all gone on vacation so im gonna be alone for a while.lol tear* At least i have Warped Tour this Wed. Last week I had my fun with them. Wed. me,hillary,bridget and david went bowling it was pretty funny. "Don't press my click..er" lol. Then Thursday night me and david went to Tower Records to buy the new Taking Back Sunday! It's such a Kickass Cd. Then Friday David took me out to eat to spend the last night together before he left. It was sweet! Well i have to go leo is playing his guitar too god damn loud!

Hopefully its kick ass like last years<3 Right now it just stopped raining and all I can think about is david lol so I'm going to go.
